# Mental Health Risk Detection Using Reddit NLP

**Author:** Salman Shareef  
**Program:** M.S. Applied Data Science  
**Course:** Practicum I  
**Institution:** University of St. Thomas  

---

## ðŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project applies Natural Language Processing (NLP) to large-scale Reddit mental health discussions to:

- Measure emotional sentiment
- Discover latent psychological themes using topic modeling
- Detect high-risk distress signals indicating severe emotional vulnerability

The goal is to demonstrate how computational text analytics can support digital mental health surveillance and public health policy.

