## ðŸ§ª Analysis Pipeline

### âœ… Notebook 1 â€” Data Ingestion & Cleaning  
- Streamed chunk processing (memory safe)
- Removal of spam, empty, deleted posts
- Text normalization & token filtering

### âœ… Notebook 2 â€” Sentiment Analysis  
- VADER polarity scoring
- Disk-based streaming sentiment computation
- Saved sentiment-enriched dataset

### âœ… Notebook 3 â€” Topic Modeling (LDA)  
- TF-IDF vectorization
- Latent Dirichlet Allocation
- Dominant psychological topic assignment

### âœ… Notebook 4 â€” Mental Health Risk Detection  
- High-risk keyword heuristic model
- Negative sentiment risk flagging
- Topic-level and time-based distress trend analysis

