## âš ï¸ Data Availability

Due to GitHub file size limits, the raw Reddit dataset (`>500MB`) and processed row-level CSVs are **not included in this repository**.  
They are generated locally using the notebooks.

---

## ðŸ“œ Ethical Disclaimer

This project performs **probabilistic risk detection only** and is **not a clinical diagnostic tool**. All data are anonymized public Reddit posts. Results are intended solely for research and policy-level insights.

